      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i'm just watching a movie of my life. like i'm sitting in a theater watching this person go through the motions, talking to people, working, eating... but i'm not actually in the seat. i'm not even in the room. it feels like the \"me\" part of me just evaporated a long time ago. there's nothing left inside the shell.",
