    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like a \"feeling\" though. like it's not some temporary mood. it's just a fact. the person everyone sees is just a costume i put on every morning so they don't ask questions. but there's nobody behind the mask anymore. it's just empty space. if i'm not even really here, what's the point of keeping up the act?",
